# 💸 Money Matters: A Friendly Expense Tracker

**Money Matters** is an emoji-powered personal finance app built with **Streamlit**, **Pandas** and **Plotly**.  
It combines playful UI flourishes with solid expense-tracking features—no database required!

> _Track your spending with style and insight. Your finances never looked so fun!_ 🎉

---

## 🚀 Core Features

- 🔐 **Tabbed Authentication**  
  – Login, Register & Recover Password in a sleek tabbed interface  
- 🌈 **Animated Gradient Background**  
  – Full-screen CSS gradient that shifts colors seamlessly  
- 🗄️ **Local JSON Storage**  
  – `users.json` for credentials/hints, `expenses.json` for your data  
- 🧠 **Time-Aware Greetings**  
  – “Good morning, money maestro!” or “Good evening, financial wizard!”  
- 🍔 🛍️ **Emoji-Rich Categories**  
  – Food, Travel, Shopping, Rent, Health, Utilities, Entertainment  
- 📊 **Interactive Charts**  
  – Pie & Bar charts with embedded emojis and hover tooltips  
- ✨ **Instant Feedback**  
  – Success toasts on account creation & expense save, formatted ₹ currency  

